> "Why don't you let me go to bring you that Autobot, Maxima?"said 
> Blackstorm"I'm willing to prove that I'm a worthy Predacon..."
> 
> 

"I know you are. But... you cannot be as risk to be captured by then either. 
You are too valuable to Hydras." She stated to the other fembot as she gazed 
at her. Hydras would never forgive her for the capture of Blackstorm. That is 
something she wanted to avoid at all costs. "No.. Battera can retreive 
Wheeljack for me. You have a more important task, Blackstorm. When Battera 
brings Wheeljack to this point, you will then in turn bring Wheeljack to my 
location." Projecting a holographic image of this current world, it then 
homed in the area they were in & indicated to an area that was unmarked but 
was an area of mountains, even volcanic. "Bring Wheekjack here. Make sure he 
does see or record the flight path. This place is not to be discovered." 

--part1_15e.1f6a1a34.2be920de_boundary
